Content-Type: text/plain

1. Open file
2. Press "Ctrl+Shift+/" (for windows)
3. Make sure that function in code in file is curled
4. Open "Preferences\JavaScript\Folding" 
5. Uncheck "Enable Folding" check-box and save changes
6. Make sure that folding is not applied in code
